<h2>What is a gastric emptying scan?</h2><p>A gastric emptying scan is a test to see how long it takes for food to empty from the stomach and enter the small intestine.</p> </div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div aria-controls="article-ProcedureOverview" aria-expanded="false" class="panel-heading clickable rs_preserve" role="button" tabindex="0">
