<span class="pull-right panel-heading-collapsable-icon" href="#article-ProcedureOverview">
<i aria-hidden="true" class="mdi mdi-chevron-down"></i>
</span>
</div>
<div class="panel-body list-group collapse out" data-propname="ProcedureOverview" id="article-ProcedureOverview" role="tabpanel" style="display: none;">
<h2>How long does the scan take?</h2>
<p>The scan (both solid and liquid) takes about 2.5 hours.</p> </div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div aria-controls="article-RisksOfTest" aria-expanded="false" class="panel-heading clickable rs_preserve" role="button" tabindex="0">
<span class="panel-heading-collapsable">Risks of the test</span>
<span class="pull-right panel-heading-collapsable-icon" href="#article-RisksOfTest">
