<div class="panel-body list-group collapse out" data-propname="FollowUpCare" id="article-FollowUpCare" role="tabpanel" style="display: none;">
<h2>When are the results available?</h2>
<p>A nuclear medicine doctor will send a report to your family doctor or paediatrician (child's doctor) within one or two working days of the scan. Please contact your doctor to get the results. You will not be able to get the results from the nuclear medicine technologist.</p> </div>
